ocused changes for `org.jboss.arquillian.core.spi.SecurityActions`.\n\nChanged files:\n- `tests/src/org.jboss.arquillian.core/arquillian-core-spi/1.1.10.Final/src/test/java/org_jboss_arquillian_core/arquillian_core_spi/SecurityActionsDynamicAccessTest.java`\n  - Added dedicated public dynamic-access test class for `SecurityActions`.\n  - Covers:\n    - default `ManagerBuilder.create()` path for `SecurityActions.loadClass(...)`\n    - fallback path when TCCL cannot load `ManagerImpl`\n    - explicit class-loader `newInstance(...)` path and constructor invocation path\n- `tests/src/org.jboss.arquillian.core/arquillian-core-spi/1.1.10.Final/build.gradle`\n  - Added `arquillian-core-impl` test dependency using the same tested `libraryVersion`, needed because `ManagerBuilder` loads `org.jboss.arquillian.core.impl.ManagerImpl`.\n- `tests/src/org.jboss.arquillian.core/arquillian-core-spi/1.1.10.Final/src/test/java/org_jboss_arquillian_core/arquillian_core_spi/Arquillian_core_spiTest.java`\n  - Made the existing top-level test class `public` to comply with the task rule.\n\nI did not compile or run tests, per instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0e39a17b4266a3130169f656bcd10c81939d7c17c63a8bae37\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1276, "output": 1013, "cacheRead": 35328, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 37617, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777751728223, "responseId": "resp_0e39a17b4266a3130169f656b164c08193abb7100b27e74e97"}, "toolResults": []}
